&lt;li&gt;Ensure accuracy of financial statements, reconciliations, and reporting integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage external accounting relationships and improve close timelines, accuracy, and automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain internal controls, audit readiness, and financial compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
